      • addTableNode

        public void addTableNode(REXPDatasetProvider provider,
                String parentName,
                String path)
        Description copied from class: MicroSimScapeNode
        Add a saveable node for a REXPDatasetProvider under the folder and subfolder specified. Creates the folder and/or subfolder if it doesn't already exist. Convenience method that can be called from R.
        Overrides:
        addTableNode in class MicroSimScapeNode
        Parameters:
        provider - provider
        parentName - name of parent to create node under. Created if it doesn't already exist.
        path - a path to a sub folder node, eg: "Base/Means" which represents the folder Means under the folder Base, or just "Base" which will add to the folder Base, or null to add directly under parentName.
